'''Chev''' was the native tongue of the [[Chev]] [[Species/Legends|species]].

The Chevs were a [[Slavery/Legends|slave]] species to the [[Chevin/Legends|Chevin]], so the Chevs also spoke [[Chevin (language)|Chevin]]. As a result, Chev language was heavily influenced by Chevin language.

Chevins usually encouraged their Chevs to practice [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], so that they become more useful and also a commodity that could be sold to other species. However, Basic influence on Chev language was only slight.

